Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:39.63,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Let's break the tight-fisted night!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:45.17,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We have no interest in treasure chests
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.43,0:01:48.64,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,A pocket of romance, and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,We are!
